@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using FuneralOfficeSystem.Models
@inject SignInManager<ApplicationUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" title="Manage">Γεια σας @User.Identity?.Name!</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Page("/", new { area = "" })" method="post">
                <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-light">Αποσύνδεση</button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register">Εγγραφή</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login">Σύνδεση</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>